        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Import of natural gas in 2021 by trade partner based on EuroStat [NRG_TI_GAS] (accessed on 2023-06-06) for countries within Europe (except GB, which was based on 'Digest of UK Energy Statistics (DUKES): natural gas', accessed on 2023-06-20), and on 'bp Statistical Review of World Energy June 2022' for the rest of the world. PVs for imports to Rest-of-Europe and GLO/Rest-of-the-World were calculated by subtracting the sum of country-specific PVs modelled separately from the total import of the respective regions.</productionVolumeComment>
